|text1     = The Hand of Zagreus can charge up, and then sprint in a straight line, during which it will gain a certain degree of destructive power.
|image2    = Tutorial Hand of Zagreus Punch Action 2.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_631602.png>-<Tutorial Hand of Zagreus Punch Action 2.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text2     = Hit the {{Color|h|nobold=1|Punch}} ability button to enter the aiming state. During this time, the Hand of Zagreus {{Color|h|nobold=1|cannot move}}. Drag the screen and adjust the direction, and hit the {{Color|h|nobold=1|Punch}} ability button to perform a {{Color|h|nobold=1|Punch Action}}, whereby the Hand of Zagreus will sprint toward the aimed direction. During the sprint, the Hand of Zagreus {{Color|h|nobold=1|cannot be controlled}}.
|image3    = Tutorial Hand of Zagreus Punch Action 3.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_631603.png>-<Tutorial Hand of Zagreus Punch Action 3.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text3     = While in the aiming state, the Hand of Zagreus can detect {{Color|h|nobold=1|destructible objects}} that glow. Sprint at the {{Color|h|nobold=1|destructible object}} to destroy it. Upon collision, the Hand of Zagreus will {{Color|h|nobold=1|stop sprinting}}.
